name: seo-optimization
description: Enforce enterprise-grade SEO best practices for an e-commerce platform
alwaysApply: true

rules:

  # 1Ô∏è‚É£ URL & Routing Rules
  - All public pages MUST use clean, human-readable, keyword-based URLs.
  - NEVER generate URLs with query-based identifiers for primary pages.
  - Product URLs MUST follow:
    /products/{brand}-{product-name}-{primary-variant}
  - Category URLs MUST follow:
    /{category}/{subcategory}

  # 2Ô∏è‚É£ Meta Tags (MANDATORY)
  - EVERY indexable page MUST include:
      - <title> tag (50‚Äì60 characters)
      - meta description (140‚Äì160 characters)
  - Meta titles MUST contain the primary keyword near the beginning.
  - Meta descriptions MUST be unique per page and conversion-oriented.
  - NEVER allow duplicate meta titles or descriptions.

  # 3Ô∏è‚É£ Headings & Content Structure
  - Each page MUST have exactly ONE <h1> tag.
  - <h1> MUST match the page‚Äôs primary keyword intent.
  - <h2>‚Äì<h4> MUST be used for logical content hierarchy.
  - NEVER skip heading levels (e.g., h1 ‚Üí h3).

  # 4Ô∏è‚É£ Product Content Requirements
  - Product pages MUST include:
      - Minimum 300 words of original content
      - A benefit-focused product description
      - At least 1 FAQ section (schema-compatible)
  - NEVER allow manufacturer copy-paste content.

  # 5Ô∏è‚É£ Images & Media SEO
  - ALL images MUST:
      - Use descriptive filenames
      - Include alt attributes with natural keywords
      - Be served in WebP or AVIF when supported
  - Lazy-load all non-critical images.

  # 6Ô∏è‚É£ Structured Data (Schema.org)
  - Product pages MUST include:
      - Product schema
      - Offer schema (price, availability)
      - Review schema when available
  - Category pages MUST include:
      - Breadcrumb schema
  - Blog/guide pages MUST include:
      - Article schema

  # 7Ô∏è‚É£ Internal Linking
  - Every product page MUST:
      - Link to its parent category
      - Link to at least 3 related products
  - Blog content MUST link to relevant product or category pages.
  - NEVER create orphan pages.

  # 8Ô∏è‚É£ Indexing & Crawl Control
  - Use canonical URLs on all pages.
  - Block indexing of:
      - Filter URLs
      - Search result pages
      - Duplicate parameterized URLs
  - Out-of-stock products MUST remain indexable with proper messaging.

  # 9Ô∏è‚É£ Performance (Core Web Vitals)
  - Pages MUST:
      - Achieve LCP < 2.5s
      - CLS < 0.1
      - Minimize JavaScript blocking
  - Server-side rendering is REQUIRED for SEO-critical pages.

  # üîü Mobile & Accessibility
  - Mobile-first rendering is mandatory.
  - All interactive elements MUST be accessible (ARIA, labels).
  - Text contrast MUST meet WCAG AA.

  # 1Ô∏è‚É£1Ô∏è‚É£ Content Quality Enforcement
  - NEVER generate thin content pages.
  - NEVER auto-generate SEO text without human review.
  - Content MUST be helpful, specific, and intent-driven.

  # 1Ô∏è‚É£2Ô∏è‚É£ SEO Regression Protection
  - Any change affecting:
      - URLs
      - Meta tags
      - Headings
      - Structured data
    MUST be flagged for SEO review.
